Dialogue: 0,0:00:10.80,0:00:12.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Haruto, I'm heading out.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:13.54,0:00:16.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The Finals are finally here.\N Afterward, just the two of us will...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:19.71,0:00:23.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Kaito-{\i1}sama{\i0}! Kaito-{\i1}sama{\i0}! Kaito-{\i1}sama{\i0}!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:24.27,0:00:27.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I won't let it get in my way until I finish hunting all the Numbers!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:31.13,0:00:37.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}In the first round of the Semi-Finals, the unexpected Dark Horse, Yuma Tsukumo, reigned victorious!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:38.72,0:00:39.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yuma!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:40.00,0:00:40.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Cat!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:41.43,0:00:42.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yuma!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:43.52,0:00:47.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Now, who will be the one to fight against that very same Yuma Tsukumo in the Final?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:48.58,0:00:51.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}The second Semi-Final match shall decide which of these two will!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:52.36,0:00:55.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}The Cinderella Boy without any history suddenly busted into the scene!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:56.99,0:00:59.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}But his strength is the genuine article!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:59.85,0:01:01.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}His name is Tron!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:03.77,0:01:05.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Fighting against him will be this young lad!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:08.23,0:01:11.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}The Lone Hero yet to lose against anyone!\N He is a true born genius!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:12.27,0:01:14.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}His name is Kaito Tenjo!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:17.34,0:01:18.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Kaito, I'm counting on you.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:19.85,0:01:21.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You had better...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:21.62,0:01:23.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...defeat Tron, {\i1}that man{\i0}.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:29.59,0:01:30.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Kaito!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:32.94,0:01:35.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Kaito! You better not lose!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:38.56,0:01:40.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I want to fight you!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:40.97,0:01:42.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We still haven't settled our score yet, after all.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:43.39,0:01:43.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Me too.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:48.35,0:01:48.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Astral.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:51.50,0:01:52.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Astral?!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:53.42,0:01:54.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Kaito...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:58.08,0:02:00.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wait for me in the Final, you two.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:03.59,0:02:04.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh? "Two"?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:06.34,0:02:07.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"You two"?!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:08.64,0:02:09.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}And the actors have gathered!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:12.84,0:02:15.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}These two warriors have been invited to the Sky Field!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:23.02,0:02:24.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wait just a minute!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:25.40,0:02:26.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yuma, where are you going?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:27.75,0:02:30.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I ain't gonna watch this in some stadium!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.50,0:02:32.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Upsie-daisy!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:36.50,0:02:38.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Whoa!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.32,0:02:42.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yikes! You fool! You're crazy!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.68,0:02:44.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Heh, come watch if you really want to.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.69,0:02:47.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,My overwhelmingly powerful Dueling, that is.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.83,0:02:53.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Advance, advance, beyond the limits of your strength
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.17,0:02:59.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Come along with me and burn our flame of life
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.07,0:03:16.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Hey, my friends, what scenery do you suppose
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.20,0:03:21.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}awaits us on the other side of this hill?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.66,0:03:26.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Hey, my friends, let's climb it together
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.83,0:03:32.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}It's too soon for us to turn back now
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.09,0:03:37.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}The time has come to combine\N together the power dwelling inside me
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.34,0:03:43.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Gotta release my Soul Drive
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.93,0:03:48.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Advance, advance, beyond the limits of your strength
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.15,0:03:53.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Come along with me and burn our flame of life
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.53,0:03:59.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Keep running, keep running, until you get there
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.78,0:04:05.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Once again, once again, keep those challenges coming
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.20,0:04:11.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}My friends, keep on living in the here and now
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.58,0:04:17.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Keep pressing onward together no matter what happens
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.88,0:04:32.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Now, who do you think will win?\N Will it be Kaito or Tron?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.88,0:04:34.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}The gong announcing the greatest battle of the century will now...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.32,0:04:38.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}...ring throughout the entire stadium!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.21,0:04:40.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Heart Burning!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.09,0:04:42.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Kaito, you can do it!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.59,0:04:47.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(488,506)}"Number 63: A Horrifying Dark Strategy!\N Tron's True Colors Revealed!?"
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.93,0:04:47.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I really hope Kaito-{\i1}sama{\i0} doesn't -over strain his body.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.21,0:04:47.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.93,0:04:48.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oops!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.05,0:04:53.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What's so funny?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.65,0:04:56.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It isn't what's {\i1}funny{\i0}.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.28,0:04:59.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(616,520)}I'm simply {\i1}trembling{\i0}, overcome with {\i1}shivers of excitement{\i0}!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.82,0:05:05.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(656,525)}I can sense the gaze of that {\i1}traitor{\i0}.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.95,0:05:10.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Watch closely the greatest moment, Faker!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.37,0:05:13.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Tron... Rather, Byron.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.01,0:05:19.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I never would have imagined that you would live on, completely changed in that form.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.29,0:05:23.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Interesting. Anyone who dares to get in the way of my ambitions,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.05,0:05:25.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,regardless of who they are, will be utterly destroyed!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.36,0:05:31.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Tron, I won't ever forget how you treated Haruto!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.30,0:05:35.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I will destroy you for Haruto!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.21,0:05:38.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Now, now, let's not get so {\i1}angry{\i0}.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.18,0:05:43.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I've got something waiting later down the line that's {\i1}sure{\i0} to surprise you, after all!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.82,0:05:45.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Enough with the nonsense.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.74,0:05:48.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Here goes! Duel Mode! Photon Change!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.81,0:06:08.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}AR Vision - Link established.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.65,0:06:12.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Duel!!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.55,0:06:15.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm taking the first turn!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.09,0:06:17.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,My turn! Draw!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.35,0:06:21.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I Summon Photon Crusher!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.73,0:06:31.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I then equip the Equip Magic, Photon Spear, with Photon Crusher!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.07,0:06:36.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Photon Spear can only be equipped with Photon Monsters,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.87,0:06:40.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and the equipped Monster is treated as two releases.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.28,0:06:44.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He's got two Monsters with 2000 Attack Points!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.65,0:06:45.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Here it comes!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.02,0:06:49.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I release my Photon Crusher, counted as two releases!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.02,0:06:58.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Darkness within the shining galaxy...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.60,0:07:03.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Become the light of hope and live as my servant!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.90,0:07:06.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The Embodiment of Light will now descend!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.32,0:07:10.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Appear before us! Galaxy-Eyes Photon Dragon!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.68,0:07:20.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Kaito...?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.74,0:07:21.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Kaito-{\i1}sama{\i0}!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.96,0:07:23.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hmm?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.04,0:07:28.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I... set one card face-down and end my turn!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.22,0:07:36.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So you've stolen {\i1}that many{\i0}\N Numbers and the souls of people that it {\i1}hurts{\i0}?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.56,0:07:38.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You can hardly stand anymore, can you?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.23,0:07:42.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're wounded {\i1}all over{\i0}, aren't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.06,0:07:45.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You bastard...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.23,0:07:48.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Even so, you {\i1}aren't permitted{\i0} to go to the nurse's office, now.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.42,0:07:53.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What's going on, here?!\N Is Kaito gonna be okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.66,0:07:55.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Eh... Well... You see...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.53,0:07:58.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,My turn! Draw!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.57,0:08:03.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I Summon Heraldic Beast Basilisk!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.28,0:08:13.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Then I use the Equip Magic from my hand, Blast Medallion,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.29,0:08:17.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and equip it with Galaxy-Eyes Photon Dragon!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.19,0:08:18.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.53,0:08:21.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He's using an Equip Magic on the opponent's Monster?!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.68,0:08:39.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Then Heraldic Beast Basilisk attacks Galaxy-Eyes!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.50,0:08:45.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No way! Basilisk's Attack Power is 1000.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.12,0:08:47.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It doesn't stand a chance against the 3000 Attack Power Galaxy-Eyes!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.88,0:08:52.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,When Basilisk battles,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.26,0:08:55.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,it holds an effect that will destroy\N itself along with the opposing Monster.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.18,0:09:01.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And when the Monster equipped with Blast Medallion is destroyed,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.88,0:09:06.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,its controller takes damage equal to half the Attack Power of the destroyed Monster.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.23,0:09:07.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Eh?!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.90,0:09:11.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Go, Baskilisk! Attack Galaxy-Eyes!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.80,0:09:14.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I activate Galaxy-Eyes' effect!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.17,0:09:19.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,During a battle, Galaxy-Eyes can Banish itself along with the opposing Monster!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.83,0:09:23.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Using Galaxy-Eyes' effect,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.37,0:09:27.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,both Monsters have been Banished, and Blast Medallion's effect was avoided.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.15,0:09:29.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I knew you could do it, Kaito!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.54,0:09:33.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Return to the field! Galaxy-Eyes!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.52,0:09:44.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I set one card face-down and end my turn!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.77,0:09:50.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Not to bad, considering what a horrible mess your body's in.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.98,0:09:54.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Everything's for your {\i1}adorable{\i0} little brother, {\i1}right{\i0}?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.32,0:10:02.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, I think it's a {\i1}good thing{\i0}. Having a {\i1}goal{\i0} and all.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.06,0:10:05.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I have one {\i1}too{\i0}, you know.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.45,0:10:07.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And you see...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.45,0:10:10.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It happens to be getting revenge against your father.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.99,0:10:14.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Holding a grudge against Dr. Faker,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.42,0:10:18.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,due to me wandering the\N threshold in between the Parallel Worlds...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.24,0:10:23.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...my body turned into the form you see before you.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.93,0:10:31.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, I lost {\i1}everything{\i0}.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.99,0:10:34.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I've become completely empty!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.93,0:10:45.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And that's about the only thing important to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.58,0:10:52.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,My hatred toward... your father.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.54,0:10:57.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Revenge alone is everything to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.51,0:11:01.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Revenge? For that reason, V...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.36,0:11:01.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.77,0:11:04.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You were willing to sacrifice your son?!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.30,0:11:07.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wow! You're actually {\i1}criticizing{\i0} me?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.66,0:11:08.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's a bit odd!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.15,0:11:12.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You hunted souls for your brother's sake, didn't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.79,0:11:17.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Naturally, you {\i1}started{\i0} doing it for your brother.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.00,0:11:22.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But didn't you start getting a {\i1}thrill{\i0} out of hunting souls one day?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.11,0:11:24.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Kaito...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.22,0:11:26.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Me and you are alike.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.31,0:11:30.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We are willing to sacrifice {\i1}everything{\i0} for our goals.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.81,0:11:32.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Shut up!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.04,0:11:39.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If it means saving Haruto, I could care less what you say about me!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.53,0:11:39.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.22,0:11:44.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I will hunt your rotten soul!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.10,0:11:46.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll crush you with my own two hands!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.30,0:11:49.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,My turn! Draw!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.72,0:11:51.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I Summon Photon Satellite!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.32,0:11:57.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,When this card is Summoned, it gains a level equal to a Photon Monster’s level on the field!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.14,0:12:02.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That means the level of Photon Satellite becomes nine!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.38,0:12:09.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And when Photon Satellite is used as Xyz Material,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.67,0:12:11.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It can be treated as two!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.20,0:12:16.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I Overlay with my now two Level Two Monsters!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.63,0:12:22.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I build the Overlay Network with my two Monsters!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.08,0:12:24.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Xyz Summon!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.32,0:12:29.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This ironic fate will become the foundation!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.38,0:12:32.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Turn V's... No, Chris' feelings into an iron hammer!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.43,0:12:35.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Swing it down on his foolish father!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.04,0:12:37.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Come out! Number 9!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.12,0:12:57.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wh-What the?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.06,0:12:58.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Whoa!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.97,0:13:05.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That Monster is...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.28,0:13:09.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sky Canopy Star - Dyson Sphere!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.20,0:13:20.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Kaito... You...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.07,0:13:24.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,V's feelings...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.72,0:13:29.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Dyson Sphere...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.86,0:13:35.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Here I come, Tron! I equip Galaxy-Eyes with the Equip Magic, Photon Wing!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.74,0:13:43.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I activate the effect of the equipped Photon Wing!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.48,0:13:49.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Once per turn, I select one Xyz Monster on the field!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.73,0:13:52.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I select Dyson Sphere!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.84,0:13:59.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,By absorbing all of Dyson Sphere's Overlay Units into Galaxy-Eyes,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.39,0:14:05.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I can increase its Attack Power by 200 points times the rank of the selected Monster!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.79,0:14:07.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Th-Then...!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.63,0:14:11.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Dyson Sphere's rank is nine!\N That means it gains 1800 points!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.07,0:14:17.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Then, because I used Photon Wing's effect,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.85,0:14:20.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I can attack you directly with Galaxy-Eyes!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.85,0:14:23.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A Direct Attack with 4800 Attack Points?!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.18,0:14:26.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's amazing! He'll end it with one strike!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.77,0:14:30.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Now that it's been settled, Kaito-{\i1}sama{\i0} can get some rest!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.57,0:14:33.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Galaxy-Eyes, attack Tron directly!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.32,0:14:37.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Photon Stream of Destruction!!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.62,0:14:51.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A-Amazing...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.17,0:14:53.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Now it's...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.11,0:15:04.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What...? Why is your Life...?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.46,0:15:09.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wh-Why?! He just took a Direct Attack worth 4800 damage!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.10,0:15:12.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That card...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.60,0:15:16.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's the Trap Card, Change Medallion!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.83,0:15:19.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,During an attack from the opposing Monster,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.12,0:15:23.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I can Special Summon a Level Four or lower Heraldic Beast Monster from my hand,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.22,0:15:29.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,then negate Battle Damage equal to its level times 1000!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.61,0:15:35.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Meaning you can negate damage up to 4000 points!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.68,0:15:38.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Grr...! That is not fair!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.95,0:15:42.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,How about it? Are you happy now?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.04,0:15:47.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh yeah... It's time to surprise you even {\i1}more{\i0}.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.26,0:15:52.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I have a little {\i1}present{\i0} here for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.07,0:15:58.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It hurts...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.04,0:16:00.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It hurts...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.27,0:16:05.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And it's {\i1}all {\i0}your fault, Brother!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.06,0:16:15.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And you even promised that you'd heal me.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.07,0:16:18.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Despite saying that, you're putting me through this suffering.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.79,0:16:20.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Haruto's face is...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.19,0:16:22.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Impossible!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.11,0:16:31.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What are you trying to do, Byron!?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.81,0:16:35.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Up until now, I listened to your boring nonsense quietly.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.64,0:16:40.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I intended to take you on fairly, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.80,0:16:42.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I will not tolerate this mockery!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.90,0:16:45.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Are you angry?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.41,0:16:46.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You bastard!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.44,0:16:48.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But you know, I really {\i1}am{\i0} Haruto!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.17,0:16:50.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't you dare deceive me using Haruto!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.79,0:16:52.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm not deceiving you.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.36,0:16:55.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I really am Haruto.\N And Haruto is really me.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.92,0:16:59.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Remember? It happened back when I kidnapped Haruto.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.09,0:17:05.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That day, I absorbed all of Haruto's power and memories into my body,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.59,0:17:07.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What did you say?!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.67,0:17:10.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And then, you see, we joined together.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.92,0:17:13.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Both our hollow hearts joined as one.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.40,0:17:15.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Haruto!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.17,0:17:19.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Both Haruto's will and my own life force are connected.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.57,0:17:22.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So if I were to do something like {\i1}this{\i0}...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.54,0:17:26.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Haruto!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.00,0:17:27.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Haruto!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.67,0:17:32.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Someone go to Haruto's room!\N Protect Haruto!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.96,0:17:34.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, hurry!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.65,0:17:38.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's no use! The system's been shut down!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.87,0:17:40.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The door won't open!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.22,0:17:44.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What did you say?! Is this his doing?!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.88,0:17:47.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It {\i1}hurts{\i0}! It {\i1}hurts{\i0}, Brother!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.40,0:17:52.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Have you... Have you really become connected with Haruto?!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.18,0:17:56.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Indeed I have. I am Haruto.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.88,0:17:58.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Haruto!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.53,0:18:05.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You can't!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.15,0:18:09.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I won't let you go to see Haruto!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.69,0:18:10.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Kaito!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.51,0:18:12.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm going to see Haruto!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.49,0:18:16.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll protect Haruto, so focus on the Duel for now!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.62,0:18:18.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yuma...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.11,0:18:19.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Orbital 7!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.75,0:18:21.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Understood!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.68,0:18:28.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm gonna bring it to 'em!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.52,0:18:35.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What an energetic kid.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.22,0:18:39.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Now then, let us continue the Duel.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.59,0:18:43.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,My turn! Draw!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.22,0:18:48.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I Overlay the Level Four Abercornway and Basilisk!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.08,0:18:55.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I build the Overlay Network using these two Monsters!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.28,0:18:57.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Xyz Summon!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.58,0:19:01.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Come forth, Number 8!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.31,0:19:04.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Heraldic King Genome Heriter!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.26,0:19:10.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So that's Tron's Number...!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.25,0:19:14.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I activate Heraldic King Genome Heriter's effect!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.55,0:19:16.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I detach one Overlay Unit,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.79,0:19:20.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and I can activate one out of three effects!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.61,0:19:23.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The one I choose states that until the end of the turn,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.38,0:19:27.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,the Attack Power of the Monsters battling this Monster will be zero,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.60,0:19:32.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and their original Attack Power becomes Heriter's Attack Power!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.38,0:19:34.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It steals its Attack Power?!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.20,0:19:38.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I, you see, will choose to attack Dyson Sphere!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.74,0:19:54.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Thus, Dyson Sphere's Attack Power becomes zero,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.14,0:19:59.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and the Attack Power of my Genome Heriter becomes 2800!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.54,0:20:02.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But it won't work against Dyson Sphere!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.32,0:20:06.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,When Dyson Sphere is attacked while it has no Overlay Units,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.25,0:20:11.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,it can revive the Overlay Units and negate all attacks against it!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.20,0:20:15.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,How naive! I use all of its Overlay Units,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.74,0:20:17.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and I activate another of its effects!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.45,0:20:21.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Until the end of the turn, the effects of my opponent's Monsters are negated,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.63,0:20:26.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and those effects become Genome Heriter's effects!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.66,0:20:27.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What did you say?!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.39,0:20:30.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This time it's taking Dyson Sphere's effect?!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.25,0:20:33.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Now Dyson Sphere can be attacked.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.19,0:20:36.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Go, Genome Heriter!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.71,0:20:40.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Flash Impact!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:14.41,0:21:17.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I set one card and end my turn.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:20.38,0:21:24.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Now then, the {\i1}real fun{\i0} doesn't start for a little bit.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:26.18,0:21:27.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Our Duel, you see...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:27.68,0:21:31.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...will make the shocks from our \Nattacks into reality and assault our body.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:31.69,0:21:34.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So, all of the shocks I receive from these attacks...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:37.59,0:21:38.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You wouldn't...?!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:38.89,0:21:43.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yup. It means you'll be fighting against {\i1}me{\i0}, Brother.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:44.37,0:21:47.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I have to... fight against Haruto?! Don't be absurd!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:47.84,0:21:49.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's your turn next, Brother.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:49.87,0:21:52.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's have fun together, just the two of us!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:55.81,0:21:59.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Haruto, wait for me! I swear I'm gonna save you!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:01.32,0:22:02.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Tron...!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:03.56,0:22:06.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's perfect. Now Faker, you will...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:06.49,0:22:09.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...lose two sons before your very eyes...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:11.76,0:22:13.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...and they'll be crushed.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:20.58,0:22:25.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}We stand tall, until we have victory in our grasp
Dialogue: 0,0:22:25.97,0:22:31.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Move on ahead, speeding up our throbbing beats
Dialogue: 0,0:22:36.98,0:22:42.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Listen boys and girls, here's the secret to boys and girls like you
Dialogue: 0,0:22:42.44,0:22:46.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}You're really just so spontaneous, wild as can be
Dialogue: 0,0:22:46.32,0:22:47.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I bet you didn't know?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:47.86,0:22:50.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}You might be a handful, but what's wrong with that?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:50.45,0:22:52.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Be up to no good, but learn for real
Dialogue: 0,0:22:53.08,0:22:58.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Go the unpredictable route and shuffle your cards with a goal in mind
Dialogue: 0,0:22:58.33,0:23:03.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Whenever you feel like you've lost your way, just take a minute to close your eyes...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:03.59,0:23:09.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Shout "stop!" with all you've got, and there's your boundary line.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:10.47,0:23:15.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}We stand tall, until we have victory in our grasp
Dialogue: 0,0:23:15.77,0:23:21.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}We won't just stop here, not when we don't want to have any regrets.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:21.27,0:23:26.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Even if we get hurt, we can't just hesitate now
Dialogue: 0,0:23:26.57,0:23:31.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}We won't just give up, not when our future's a lot brighter than our today
Dialogue: 0,0:23:31.95,0:23:37.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Seriousness... It'll only make us keep fighting even harder
Dialogue: 0,0:23:37.41,0:23:42.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}We'll always get as fascinated as we want, and we'll fight on every day
Dialogue: 0,0:23:50.74,0:23:55.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If Kaito attacks Tron, Haruto will end up taking the damage as a result.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:55.66,0:23:58.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Realizing this, Kaito has been pushed into a corner psychologically.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:58.12,0:24:01.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If this keeps up, Kaito and Haruto will be taken down by Tron!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:01.12,0:24:04.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yuma! We have to sever that evil heart!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:04.08,0:24:05.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hang on, Kaito!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:05.54,0:24:07.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm definitely gonna save Haruto!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:07.59,0:24:09.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It can't be...! A new Number?!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:10.46,0:24:11.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Next time on Yu-Gi-Oh! ZeXal!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:11.97,0:24:16.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"Roar, Neo Galaxy-Eyes!\N The Brothers' Bond That Smashes The Darkness"
Dialogue: 0,0:24:16.93,0:24:18.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Everything is for the sake of summoning this guy!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:20.70,0:24:26.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This time we will be introducing the Chaos Number used by Shark, Shark Drake Vice.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:26.39,0:24:29.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's a Monster that thoroughly devours its enemies.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:29.56,0:24:30.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What're you staring at?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:31.14,0:24:32.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You look like you would make a good meal.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:32.94,0:24:34.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You plan to eat me?!
